    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Add the <strong>radish quarters</strong> and <strong>cucumber rounds</strong> to a small bowl with the <strong>cucumber slices</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped dill</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, then give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>dill, cucumber & radish pickles</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled cucumber rounds</strong></p>",
