    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a high heat</p><p>Pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper, then drizzle them with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>on both sides</p>",
