    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until hot and crusty</p><p>Carefully slice in half before serving</p><p>Once rested, slice the <strong>cooked steak</strong> as thinly as you can on a clean board</p>",
