      "instruction": "<p>Stuff your <strong>hot ciabatta</strong> with the<strong> sliced steak</strong>, <strong>pickled radish slaw</strong> and the<strong> quick-pickled cucumber rounds</strong></p><p>Serve with the<strong> smoky potatoes </strong>and the<strong> dill, cucumber & radish pickles</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
